hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bbd2800394bf0674ded88ffd822925db7e2b57","tid":666307,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>此舉引發呼籲對中興通訊施以更多限制的國會議員不滿，有些議員指控中興通訊和其他中國企業製造出來的設備恐對網路安全構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n美國聯邦眾議院軍事委員會主席索恩貝里（Mac Thornberry）說：「我承認，在這一方面，我不完全理解政府的做法。對我而言，這不是經濟問題，而是安全問題。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201805160043-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F201805160043-1.aspx&d=pPGJYqMZWzvH3DasdLYL2UzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=84f6cb18\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201805160043-1.aspx</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw, twitter 陣間 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a8d0864fac0d99a5649504fc55252fa3e41721","tid":666307,"uid":29880,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"聽日trump:<br />\n嗱,唔關我事架,國會叫我制裁架咋,btw,我仍然好專重習總<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b58338810b662313976e4616de28b5460e1afea","tid":666307,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"邊個鬧侵反侵，邊個就係左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b699d23b96c8248211dd405eb22fbd8b3951860","tid":666307,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a8d0864fac0d99a5649504fc55252fa3e41721","tid":666307,"uid":29880,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"聽日trump:<br />\n嗱,唔關我事架,國會叫我制裁架咋,btw,我仍然好專重習總<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T17:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accf5480c62acc9bb41418d7af4184dba800eb79","tid":666307,"uid":22913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cite